        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="AppеҗҜеҠЁжөҒзЁӢ"><a href="#AppеҗҜеҠЁжөҒзЁӢ" class="headerlink" title="AppеҗҜеҠЁжөҒзЁӢ"></a>AppеҗҜеҠЁжөҒзЁӢ</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">participant Activity</span><br><span class="line">participant Instrumentation</span><br><span class="line">participant AMS</span><br><span class="line">participant ActivityStarter</span><br><span class="line">participant ActivityStackSupervisor</span><br><span class="line">participant Looper</span><br><span class="line">participant ActivityThread</span><br><span class="line">participant ActivityManager</span><br><span class="line">participant BinderInternal</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Activity-&gt;Instrumentation:startActivityForResult()</span><br><span class="line">Instrumentation-&gt;AMS:startActivity()</span><br><span class="line">AMS-&gt;ActivityStarter:startActivityAsUser()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStarter:execute()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStarter:startActivityMayWait()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStackSupervisor:getActivityMetricsLogger().notifyActivityLaunching()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStackSupervisor:resolveIntent():ResolveInfo</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStackSupervisor:resolveActivity():ActivityInfo</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStackSupervisor:mFocusedStack:ActivityStack</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStarter:startActivity()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;AMS:getRecordForAppLocked()жЈҖжҹҘи°ғз”ЁиҖ…жҳҜеҗҰеӯҳеңЁе№¶иҺ·еҸ–и°ғз”ЁиҖ…pidе’Ңuid</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStackSupervisor:isInAnyStackLocked(token)йҖҡиҝҮи°ғз”ЁstartActivityйЎөйқўзҡ„mTokenиҺ·еҸ–и°ғз”ЁиҖ…зҡ„ActivityRecord</span><br><span class="line">note over ActivityStarter:жЈҖжҹҘintent.getFlags()</span><br><span class="line">note over ActivityStarter:жЈҖжҹҘintent.getComponent()</span><br><span class="line">note over ActivityStarter:жЈҖжҹҘActivityInfo</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStackSupervisor:checkStartAnyActivityPermission()жЈҖжҹҘжҳҜеҗҰжңүеҗҜеҠЁжқғйҷҗ</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;AMS:mIntentFirewall.checkStartActivity()жЈҖжҹҘжҳҜеҗҰжңүиў«IntentйҳІзҒ«еўҷжӢҰжҲӘ</span><br><span class="line">note over ActivityStarter:ж–°е»әActivityRecord</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStarter:startActivity()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityStarter-&gt;ActivityStarter:startActivityUnchecked()пјҢе…ҲеӨ„зҗҶCLEAR_TOPжғ…еҶөпјҢ</span><br><span class="line">ActivityThread-&gt;ActivityThread: main()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityThread-&gt;Looper:prepareMainLooper()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityThread-&gt;ActivityThread: attach()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityThread-&gt;ActivityManager: getService()</span><br><span class="line">ActivityManager--&gt;ActivityThread: IActivityManager(AMS)</span><br><span class="line">ActivityThread-&gt;AMS: attachApplication()</span><br><span class="line">AMS-&gt;AMS: attachApplicationLocked()</span><br><span class="line">note right of AMS:attachApplicationLockedжҹҘжүҫProcessRecord</span><br><span class="line">ActivityThread-&gt;BinderInternal: addGcWatcher()</span><br><span class="line">note right of BinderInternal: еҪ“ dalvikUsed&gt;3*dalvikMax/4 ж—¶\nи°ғз”ЁAMS.releaseSomeActivities()\nйҮҠж”ҫеҶ…еӯҳ\nи§ҰеҸ‘иў«йҮҠж”ҫAppзҡ„LowMemoryKill</span><br><span class="line">ActivityThread-&gt;Looper:loop()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
